# textdomain: mcl_beds
Beds allow you to sleep at night and make the time pass faster.=入夜後，你可以在床上睡覺，快進到早上。
To use a bed, stand close to it and right-click the bed to sleep in it. Sleeping only works when the sun sets, at night or during a thunderstorm. The bed must also be clear of any danger.=要在床上睡覺，靠近床並右鍵點擊。只有在太陽落山時，入晚後，或雷雨時才能睡覺。床也必須遠離任何危險。
You have heard of other worlds in which a bed would set the start point for your next life. But this world is not one of them.=你聽說過在其他的世界，床會成為你的重生點。但這個世界並不這樣運作。
By using a bed, you set the starting point for your next life. If you die, you will start your next life at this bed, unless it is obstructed or destroyed.=只要使用床，就能設定重生點。如果你死了，你將在這張床上重生，除非它被阻塞或破壞。
In this world, going to bed won't skip the night, but it will skip thunderstorms.=在這個世界，上床睡覺不會跳過夜晚，但是會跳過雷暴。
Sleeping allows you to skip the night. The night is skipped when all players in this world went to sleep. The night is skipped after sleeping for a few seconds. Thunderstorms can be skipped in the same manner.=睡覺可以跳過夜晚。當這個世界的所有玩家都進入睡眠狀態後再過幾秒，夜晚就會被跳過。雷雨也可以用同樣的方式跳過。
